Shampoonaiza Comedy Show: Thapelo “Tips” Seemise, better known as Shampoonaiza, presents a collective of comedians showcasing their humorous genius in all official South African languages. Details: The show will take place on February 9 at the South African State Theatre in Pretoria. Tickets cost R200 and can be purchased from here.
